<subSubSection pageId="126" pageNumber="127" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="126.[189,303,999,1025]" box="[189,303,999,1025]" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,303,999,1025]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="126" pageNumber="127" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,999,1025]" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="126.[189,1399,1046,1144]" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">
Currently, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Shamshev &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2006" box="[314,484,1046,1073]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Stilpon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angkorensis">
<emphasis box="[314,484,1046,1073]" italics="true" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">S. angkorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only from 
<collectingCountry box="[729,854,1046,1072]" name="Cambodia" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
. However, its occurrence in 
<collectingCountry box="[1187,1306,1046,1072]" name="Singapore" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">Singapore</collectingCountry>
is quite possible. This species belongs to the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1965" box="[632,776,1082,1108]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Stilpon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="divergens">
<emphasis box="[632,776,1082,1108]" italics="true" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">S. divergens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group and is comparable to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Shamshev &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2006" box="[1119,1211,1082,1108]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Stilpon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="goesi">
<emphasis box="[1119,1211,1082,1108]" italics="true" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">S. goesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(also described from 
<collectingCountry box="[253,378,1117,1144]" name="Cambodia" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
), but can be distinguished as given in the key.
</paragraph>
